Only accessible from the home session
-------------------------------------

+ func makeAppRoute(appHash) securityCode
    So the input should be {apphash: <base64 encoded 32-byte hash>}
    And the response is a unicode-encoded random string.
+ func getApp()
    Request to localhost:3000/getapp/securityCode
+ func saveApp() appHash
+ func sendApp(appHash, recipients [][]byte)
+ func setMetadata(tags []string, accessList [][]byte, appHash []byte)
+ func searchApps(tags []string, searchString string) metadata


Accessible from all sessions
----------------------------

+ func sendMsg(msg []byte)
+ func writeFile(fileName string, contents []byte) error
+ func readFile(fileName string) ([]byte, error)
+ func quota() (spaceused int, spacefree int)
